data.description: Discover the epitome of luxurious living in this stunning home nestled within the highly desired community of Stonegate. The open concept design seamlessly blends functionality with style, creating an ideal setting for both entertaining and relaxation. In addition to the spacious three bedrooms upstairs, you'll find plenty of space with the main level den along with the bonus room upstairs featuring a versatile nook that could easily serve as a fourth bedroom. Enjoy the covered patio looking out to the natural landscaped community common area with direct access to the walking trails through your back gate. This premiere neighborhood along with the walking trails also features a community pool & playground and is just minutes to everything you may need.
